'''Josh Radke''' is the author of ''[[Who's Who in Echo Base]]'' in [[Star Wars Insider 74|''Star Wars Insider'' 74]] and ''[[Wraith Squadron: The Dirty Dozen of Star Wars|Wraith Squadron: The Dirty Dozen of ''Star Wars'']]'' in [[Star Wars Gamer 9|''Star Wars Gamer'' 9]].

He is a member of the [http://www.myuselessknowledge.com/swfa Star Wars Fanboy Association], a retired member of [[Decipher, Inc.|Decipher's]] Red Squadron volunteer corps (for the [[Star Wars Customizable Card Game]]), and co-founder of [http://grailquestbooks.com Grail Quest Books].

